                        "name": "Compel Courage",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The ostiarius inspires their willing allies and themself by whispering words of courage from their wounds. The ostiarius and their allies in a 50-foot emanation gain a +1 status bonus to attack rolls, damage rolls, and saves against fear effects. The ostiarius can Sustain Compel Courage. Non-velstracs who accept this compelled courage find bleeding wounds opening on their own bodies to whisper in thanks. They take 1 <a aonid=\"29\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">persistent bleed damage</a> and can't attempt a flat check to end this damage as long as they're compelled.",
